      <title>热门就业数据削弱美联储降息预期，美国国债收益率飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/treasuries-yields-surge-as-hot-jobs-data-dim-fed-rate-cut-bets</link>
